title: Percent Health Seals
body: I was checking the rune page in the store the other day and noticed that percent health seals (0.5% at tier 3) are missing. I checked out the quintessence section and the percent health quints are still there. I'm not particularly worried, since I already have percent health seals, but I was just wondering if anyone else noticed, or if there was a particular reason they aren't there?

replies.body: if you have a full set it wont show. unless you uncheck already owned
Yep, there it is. Thanks for helping me see my derp!
